lt |\\n| 4 | **DoubleTree by Hilton \u2013 Arpora / Baga** | 20\u202fMar\u202f2026 (2\u202fadults) | **Deluxe King** | **Expedia** | **$88** | ~\u20b9\u202f7\u202f300 | Taxes & resort fee (~12\u202f%) **not** included \u2192 final \u2248 **$99 / \u20b9\u202f8\u202f200**. Breakfast optional (INR\u202f1\u202f200). | Expedia listing |\\n| 5 | **Radisson Goa \u2013 Candolim** | 10\u202fApr\u202f2026 (2\u202fadults) | **Superior** | **Hotels.com** | **$78** | ~\u20b9\u202f6\u202f450 | Taxes & service charge (~13\u202f%) excluded \u2192 final \u2248 **$88 / \u20b9\u202f7\u202f300**. Breakfast not included (INR\u202f1\u202f200). | Hotels.com result |\\n| 6 | **Novotel Goa \u2013 Candolim (Family\u2011friendly 5\u2011star)** | 01\u202fMay\u202f2026 (2\u202fadults) | **Family Suite** | **Tripadvisor** (price quoted by a traveler) | **$137** | ~\u20b9\u202f11\u202f300 | **All\u2011inclusive** (taxes & fees already in the $137). Breakfast **included** (value INR\u202f1\u202f200). | Tripadvisor \u201cBook Now\u201d widget |\\n| 7 | **Novotel Goa \u2013 Candolim (budget\u2011style)** | 02\u202fJun\u202f2026 (2\u202fadults) | **Standard Room** | **Agoda** (alternative listing) | **$76.10** (ex\u2011tax) | ~\u20b9\u202f6\u202f300 | Same tax/fee rule as #1 \u2192 final \u2248 **$88 / \u20b9\u202f7\u202f300**. Breakfast extra. | Agoda deal page |\\n| 8 | **Novotel Goa \u2013 Candolim** (average market price) | \u2013 | \u2013 | **Statista/Market\u2011watch** (2025\u20112026 data) | **$87** (average) | ~\u20b9\u202f7\u202f200 | This is the **average** nightly price across all room categories **including** taxes & fees. | Statista report |\\n\\n\\\\* **Sample stay date** is the date that the price was displayed in the source (or the earliest date the system allowed you to pick). Prices can shift by \u00b110\u202f% depending on the exact night, length of stay, and promotional codes.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### How to Use This Sheet\\n\\n| Goal | Which rows to focus on | Why |\\n|------|------------------------|-----|\\n| **Cheapest possible night** | **#1** (Superior, $72) \u2013 but remember you\u2019ll still need to add ~15\u202f% taxes/fees. | Lowest base rate on a reputable OTA. |\\n| **All\u2011inclusive (taxes + breakfast)** | **#3** ($75 total) or **#6** ($137 all\u2011incl.) | No surprise add\u2011ons at checkout. |\\n| **Best value for a 5\u2011star experience** | **#6** ($137 all\u2011incl.) vs. market average $87 \u2013 you get a suite + breakfast + taxes for a modest premium. | Higher room class with everything bundled. |\\n| **Mid\u2011range with brand loyalty points** | **#4** (DoubleTree) or **#5** (Radisson) \u2013 both Hilton & Radisson reward programs. | Earn points for future stays; rates are competitive. |\\n| **If you need an airport shuttle** | All hotels charge **INR\u202f3\u202f600 (\u2248\u202f$48)** one\u2011way for a vehicle up to 5 pax. Add this to the final nightly cost if you plan to use it. | Shuttle fee is **separate** from room price. |\\n| **Breakfast budgeting** | Breakfast is **INR\u202f1\u202f200 per adult** (\u2248\u202f$15) at most 5\u2011star hotels in Goa. Add this to any \u201croom\u2011only\u201d rate. | Most deals list \u201croom only\u201d. |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Quick Cost\u2011Calculator (per night, 2 adults)\\n\\n| Hotel | Base rate (USD) | Taxes\u202f+\u202fResort fee (\u2248\u202f15\u202f%) | Breakfast (2\u202f\u00d7\u202fINR\u202f1\u202f200 \u2248\u202f$30) | Airport shuttle (one\u2011way) | **Total per night (USD)** |\\n|-------|----------------|----------------------------|-------------------------------|---------------------------|---------------------------|\\n| **Novotel \u2013 Superior (Agoda)** | $72 | $10.8 | $30 | $48 (if needed) | **$120.8** (\u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f10\u202f000) |\\n| **Novotel \u2013 King (Agoda)** | $82 | $12.3 | $30 | $48 | **$132.3** |\\n| **Novotel \u2013 Standard (Agoda $76.1)** | $76.1 | $11.4 | $30 | $48 | **$125.5** |\\n| **DoubleTree \u2013 Deluxe King** | $88 | $11.3 | $30 | $48 | **$137.3** |\\n| **Radisson \u2013 Superior** | $78 | $10.1 | $30 | $48 | **$126.1** |\\n| **Novotel \u2013 Family Suite (all\u2011incl.)** | $137 | 0 (included) | 0 (included) | $48 | **$185** |\\n| **Average market price** | $87 | $13.0 | $30 | $48 | **$178** |\\n\\n> **Tip:** If you\u2019re traveling with a small group (\u2264\u202f5 people) and need the shuttle, consider hiring a **single\u2011vehicle taxi** from the airport (\u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f2\u202f000 / $26) \u2013 cheaper than the hotel\u2011run shuttle.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## What\u2019s Missing for **2024**?\\n\\nYour original query mentioned \u201cMissing: 2024 | Show results with:2024\u201d.  \\n- **Why it\u2019s missing:** Most OTA APIs (Agoda, Booking.com, Expedia) default to showing the **next 30\u2011day window**; historic 2024 pricing isn\u2019t retained in the public search results.  \\n- **How to retrieve:**  \\n  1. Use the **Wayback Machine** on the specific OTA URL (e.g., `https://www.agoda.com/novotel-goa-resort-spa-candolim/hotel/goa-in.html`) and select snapshots from 2024.  \\n  2. Or contact the hotel\u2019s **sales team** directly \u2013 they can provide a \u201chistorical rate sheet\u201d for 2024 for corporate or group bookings.  \\n\\nIf you need exact 2024 numbers for a report, let me know and I can draft a short email template you can send to the hotel\u2019s revenue\u2011management department.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Bottom Line for Your Budget\\n\\n| Desired spend per night (incl. taxes, breakfast, shuttle) | Best match |\\n|-----------------------------------------------------------|------------|\\n| **\u2264\u202f$120** (\u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f10\u202f000) | **Novotel \u2013 Superior** (Agoda) \u2013 add taxes & breakfast \u2192 $120.8 |\\n| **\u2248\u202f$130** (\u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f11\u202f000) | **Novotel \u2013 King** (Agoda) or **Radisson \u2013 Superior** |\\n| **All\u2011inclusive, no surprise fees** | **Novotel \u2013 Standard (Booking.com $75 total)** \u2013 just add breakfast if you want it. |\\n| **Luxury 5\u2011star with breakfast** | **Novotel \u2013 Family Suite** ($137 all\u2011incl.) \u2013 still under $150/night. |\\n\\nFeel free to tell me which tier you\u2019d like to lock in, and I can generate a **ready\u2011to\u2011book checklist** (promo codes, cancellation policy, loyalty\u2011point notes, etc.). Happy booking! \ud83c\udf34\u2708\ufe0f\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"},\"inner_messages\":[]},\"name\":\"Travel_Planner\"}", "sender": "Travel_Planner_c42977c6-7a7f-478f-bc63-3cf37ebcbcb8/c42977c6-7a7f-478f-bc63-3cf37ebcbcb8", "receiver": null, "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.DELIVER", "type": "Message"}
